hello,
this is my first project.
the purpose of this project is to build a website for a flight company

this project is divided into three parts:
1.SQLite DB
2. python
3. HTML

In another file, you will find the SQLite DB I build.

in my python part, I separated the project into two sections:
main -  the classes and functions of the methods.
scratch - the connection from python to SQLite.

list of the connection functions to each other:

Flight functions:
main functions <===> scratch functions
import_flights <---> readFlights
cheack_flight <---> getIdflight
add_flights <---> insertValues
remainingSeatsUpdate <---> UpdateSeats
updateFlight <---> UpdateFlight
deleteFlight <---> DeleteValues

Users functions:
main functions <===> scratch functions
importUsers <---> readUsers
checkUser <---> getIdUser
add_Users <---> insertValuesUser
updateUser <---> updateUser
deleteUser <---> DeleteUserValues

Tickets functions:
main functions <===> scratch functions
importTickets <---> readTickets
checkTickets <---> getIdTickets
add_Tickets <---> insertValuesTickets
deleteTickets <---> DeleteTicketsValues

Countries functions:
main functions <===> scratch functions
importCountries <---> readCountries
checkCountries <---> getIdCountries
add_Countries <---> insertValuesCountries
updateCountries <---> updateCountries
deleteCountries <---> DeleteCountriesValues

